      <tr><td style="font-weight:700;color:var(--guava-pink)"><img src="/images/mahjong-ways2/symbols/mahjong-ways2_s_scatter.webp" alt="Scatter 散佈符號" width="52" height="52" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px" loading="lazy">Scatter（散佈）</td><td>「胡」字紅色麻將牌</td><td>3+ 個觸發 Free Spin，任意位置有效</td></tr>
